text: OMG, Alev, I'm soooo sorry! I didn't get any notification about your reply! Whaaaattt! And it's from ages ago! I am soooo sorry!

I really hope you're keeping well through the lockdown! This the 4th week! Hopefully it won't go on too much longer - they're saying maybe another week or 10 days. That would be okay, if we could count down the days!!! hahaha!

How did you get on with the Blue-Zoo portfolio day? Did you get in to it - you said you weren't sure. What kind of portfolio did you get reviewed? Design? Animation? Storyboards? If you didn't get into it, maybe I can ask around some of my peers and see if they have time to take a look :slightly_smiling_face:

Again, I'm so sorry I missed your message, I feel completely awful about it. Hope you're keeping safe and well
